SELECT
  "district_name" as "District Name",
  "district_short_code" as "District Shortcode",
  "id" as "Job ID",
  "status" as "Status",
  "created_at" as "Created At",
  "started_at" as "Started At"
FROM
  jobs
WHERE
  status not in ('completed', 'errored', 'aborted')
  AND $__timeFilter(created_at)
ORDER BY
  "Started At" asc,
  "Created At" asc;
SELECT * FROM INFORMATION_SCHEMA.COLUMNS WHERE TABLE_NAME = 'jobs' AND COLUMN_NAME = 'ended_at';

SELECT
  started_at AS "time",
  district_short_code,
  EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM (completed_at - started_at)) as "Time In Process"
FROM jobs
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(started_at)
ORDER BY 1

-- EPOCH FROM '04:30:25'::time

SELECT
  created_at AS "time",
  district_short_code,
  EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM (ended_at - created_at)) as "Time In Process"
FROM jobs
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(created_at)
ORDER BY 1
